headline: Phillips 66 (PSX) Reports Q1 Loss, Tops Revenue Estimates
summary: Phillips 66 (PSX) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -16.88% and 3.49%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
